data.description: Just completed, full renovation with additional 1360 sq ft (per assessor) of basement with newly finished rec room, alcove/office, a full bath, two newly carpeted, possible bedrooms and plenty of storage. Improvements include: 12/2020: New tear off roof, gutters, downspouts, fascia, concrete walkways and patio, wood fencing and furnace. 2021: New A/C unit. Completed 11/2022: Fully renovated kitchen with white shaker cabinetry, island, butcher block counters, hammered copper farm sink, copper cabinet hardware, new stainless steel appliances. Two full and one half bath were fully renovated and completed in October, 2023. Additional recent improvements include all interior and exterior doors, professionally installed or refinished flooring, new lighting, new garden shed. The home has insulated windows (date unknown). High quality craftsmanship and materials throughout. 35' x 35' garden for home grown vegetables or flowers. A fabulous private sanctuary that is near to forest preserves with hiking/biking trails while also convenient to shopping, restaurants and entertainment. Nothing to do, but move right in and make this house your home.
